ğŸ“‹ Application Description

The Health Care Provider Application is a desktop-based system developed using Python and Tkinter that helps manage basic healthcare operations such as patient registration and appointment scheduling.

This application is designed for small clinics, healthcare centers, or educational purposes to demonstrate how a healthcare management system works.

ğŸ¯ Purpose of the Application

The main objective of this application is to:

Digitally store patient information

Manage appointment bookings

Reduce manual paperwork

Improve clinic workflow efficiency

It provides a simple and user-friendly interface for healthcare staff to manage essential patient data.

